definitions.definition: The person or thing in the seventh position.
One of seven equal parts of a whole.
A tone of the seventh degree from a given tone, the interval between two such tones, or the two tones sounding in unison.

main_definition: The person or thing in the seventh position.
secondary_definitions: One of seven equal parts of a whole.
